 class="ds-related-work--metadata"><a class="js-wsj-grid-card-author ds2-5-body-sm ds2-5-body-link" data-author-id="305151063" href="https://independent.academia.edu/ZsuzsaV%C3%A1rhalmi">Zsuzsa Várhalmi</a></div><p class="ds-related-work--metadata ds2-5-body-xs">Educational Alternatives, 2014</p><p class="ds2-5-body-sm ds-related-work--abstract ">and Technology (EIT) acts as a driving force for implementing the Knowledge Triangle in the Central and Eastern European region. The EIT ICT Labs Master School&#39;s double degree programmes implemented at 19 European top universities, and the Doctoral Training Centres established in 6 European ICT hotspots offer an integrated education of technical knowledge and innovation &amp; entrepreneurship skills by linking together education, research and business.</p><div class="ds-related-work--ctas"><a class="ds2-5-text-link ds2-5-text-link--inline js-tc-loswp--wsj-grid-card-download-pdf-modal js-login-button--5f016d68"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 18px" translate="no">download</span><span class="ds2-5-text-link__content">Download free PDF</span></a><script>document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
