ANYING THE DIGITAL REVOLUTION</a><div class="ds-related-work--metadata"><a class="js-wsj-grid-card-author ds2-5-body-sm ds2-5-body-link" data-author-id="8527393" href="https://independent.academia.edu/AminElsaleh">Amin Elsaleh</a></div><p class="ds-related-work--metadata ds2-5-body-xs">POSITIONING OF THE D.S.C.E.L PROJECT IN RELATION TO INNOVATIVE PROJECTS ACCOMPANYING THE DIGITAL REVOLUTION180522, 2025</p><p class="ds2-5-body-sm ds-related-work--abstract ">The D.I.S.C.E.L.1is largely explained by the technology watch carried out by two PhD students from the University of Paris VI in 2010; link: https://www.academia.edu/79385154/POSITIONING_OF_THE_D_I_S_C_E_L_PROJECT_IN_RELATION_TO_INNOVATIVE_PROJECTS_ACCOMPANYING_THE_DIGITAL_REVOLUTION180522 The attached study positions our project in relation to the various research carried out in particular in the United States. It shows its complementarity via the innovative concept 1 Standard Modules for Intelligent Servers using Open Source utilities de Amin ELSALEH est mis à disposition selon les termes de la licence Creative Commons Paternité - Pas d’Utilisation Commerciale - Pas de Modification 3.0 non transcrit. Basé(e) sur une oeuvre à www.ediaudit.fr Les autorisations au-delà du champ de cette licence peuvent être obtenues en cliquant-ici Click there for authorisation beyond this licence scope This work is licensed under a Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivs 3.0 United States SPDF (Standard Process Description Format) created by the author of this article. POSITIONING OF THE D.S.C.E.L PROJECT IN RELATION TO INNOVATIVE PROJECTS ACCOMPANYING THE DIGITAL REVOLUTION How to position our D.I.S.C.E.L project? With the excerpts below, the link is very strong between our project and “serious games” a fashionable theme, but whose different interpretations bring it much closer to video games than to the “e-learning” of the years 2010-2015. By reading the references indicated in this summary, I realized that we can tackle several Master&#39;s subjects to deepen our project and lead to industrial tools. Automated process management on an online server with intelligent document-enabled commands is an effective way to engage all types of users without requiring advanced computer skills. Amin Elsaleh Some excerpts from the study “Society and the economy in the light of the digital revolution – May 2009” published by the Center for Strategic Analysis. Réf : http://www.strategie.gouv.fr/article.php3?id_article=999 Extrait p.36-37 « L’e-éducation progresse, les TICEs sont au cœur de la pédagogie. Les outils de formation sont interactifs, plus personnalisés et plus ludiques via la réalité augmentée. Ils permettent l’interaction (hors les cours) avec les professeurs et des interventions ciblées pour compenser, tout particulièrement, des inégalités sociales. La technologie permet que se généralisent une médecine préventive et personnalisée en fonction, par exemple, des caractéristique...</p><div class="ds-related-work--ctas"><a class="ds2-5-text-link ds2-5-text-link--inline js-tc-loswp--wsj-grid-card-download-pdf-modal js-login-button--87e2d232"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 18px" translate="no">download</span><span class="ds2-5-text-link__content">Download free PDF</span></a><script>document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
