li class="ordered-list--item ds2-5-body-md">D. M. Russell, &quot;Simple is Good: Observations of Visualization Use Amongst the Big Data Digerati&quot; in Proceedings of the 13 th International Working Conference on Advanced Visual Interfaces, AVI 2016, Bari, Italy, 2016, pp. 7-12.</li><li class="ordered-list--item ds2-5-body-md">ISO/IEC 9241-210, 2010. Ergonomics of human-system interaction - Part 210: Human-centred design for interactive systems. DMS2016 Authors&#39; Index</li></ol><button class="ds2-5-button ds2-5-button--extra-small ds2-5-button--full-width js-tc-loswp--references-view-more references--view-more-link" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.add(&#39;references--show-all&#39;);">View more<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 20px" translate="no">arrow_downward</span></button><script>document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
