s2_W7r AboutTheAuthorsSection-cls1_Oh8 material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:18px" translate="no">arrow_forward</span></a></section></div></div>
<script type="application/json" class="js-react-on-rails-component" id="js-react-on-rails-component-AboutTheAuthorsSSR-react-component-67d90fe4-5cfb-4099-944e-44160c00947f" data-component-name="AboutTheAuthorsSSR" data-dom-id="AboutTheAuthorsSSR-react-component-67d90fe4-5cfb-4099-944e-44160c00947f">{"authors":[{"id":162135000,"displayName":"Moonis Ali","bio":"","photo":"//a.academia-assets.com/images/s65_no_pic.png","url":"https://independent.academia.edu/MoonisAli2","position":null,"university":null,"followers":8,"papers":60,"following":false,"show_premium_badge":false}],"workId":54045043}</script><div class="safe-right-rail--related-works"><h2 class="safe-related-content--heading">Related papers</h2><div class="safe-related-content--container" data-nosnippet=""><div class="ds-related-work--container js-related-work-sidebar-card js-safe-related-work-related-work " data-collection-position="0" data-entity-id="86856433" data-sort-order="default"><a class="ds-related-work--title js-related-work-grid-card-title ds2-5-body-md ds2-5-body-link" href="https://www.academia.edu/86856433/Data_Scientist_The_Engineer_of_the_Future">Data Scientist: The Engineer of the Future</a><div class="ds-related-work--metadata"><a class="js-related-work-grid-card-author ds2-5-body-sm ds2-5-body-link" data-author-id="359324" href="https://rwth-aachen.academia.edu/WilvanderAalst">Wil van der Aalst</a></div><p class="ds2-5-body-sm ds-related-work--abstract hide-on-large">Although our capabilities to store and process data have been increasing exponentially since the 1960-ties, suddenly many organizations realize that survival is not possible without exploiting available data intelligently. Out of the blue, &quot;Big Data&quot; has become a topic in board-level discussions. The abundance of data will change many jobs across all industries. Moreover, also scientific research is becoming more data-driven. Therefore, we reflect on the emerging data science discipline. Just like computer science emerged as a new discipline from mathematics when computers became abundantly available, we now see the birth of data science as a new discipline driven by the torrents of data available today. We believe that the data scientist will be the engineer of the future. Therefore, Eindhoven University of Technology (TU/e) established the Data Science Center Eindhoven (DSC/e). This article discusses the data science discipline and motivates its importance.</p><div class="ds-related-work--ctas"><a class="ds2-5-text-link ds2-5-text-link--inline js-tc-loswp--wsj-grid-card-download-pdf-modal js-login-button--085cf6de"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size: 18px" translate="no">download</span><span class="ds2-5-text-link__content">Download free PDF</span></a><script>document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
